================
Arch及衍生类系统
================

安装
----

运行时依赖
..........
Gtk+
gst0.10及相关插件包

编译时依赖
..........
gtk2-devel
gcc
gstreamer-devel
make
cmake
libnotify-devel

编译安装
........
[iceplayer]$./build.sh
[iceplayer]$cd Build
[Build]$sudo make install

卸载软件
........
[iceplayer]$cd Build
[Build]$sudo make uninstall

